    "category": "Formula",
    "text": "$$\nMN = \\sqrt{(0-a)^2 + [a-(5-a)]^2 + (a-0)^2} = \\sqrt{6a^2 - 20a + 25} = \\sqrt{6\\left(a-\\frac{5}{3}\\right)^2 + \\frac{25}{3}} \\geq \\frac{5\\sqrt{3}}{3}.\n$$"
